data.description: Beautifully kept single level living in convenient location. Very open main floor layout with beautiful vaulted ceilings combining the kitchen, dining, & living room. Master bedroom also has a vaulted ceiling with a spacious walk-in closet. Master bath includes a double sink, walk-in shower and a large tub. Main floor also has a second bedroom/office with full bath, and a laundry room. Beautiful deck off the dining area with lattice and sunshades. A very spacious basement includes two large bedrooms a full bath and an oversized family room, perfect for large gatherings. Attached two car garage. All information including square footage is provided as a courtesy. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measure.
